/\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to download the plugin</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>We&#8217;ve added a number of few features and fixed a number of painful bugs. More importantly, we&#8217;ve done lots of ground work that will allow us to roll out new versions faster.</p>\n<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Recurring Events now shows the date and time of the current event rather then the original event.</li>\n<li>Events posted across the Daylight Savings time line were wrong. That&#8217;s fixed.</li>\n<li>We&#8217;ve globalized the date picker (Thanks josjo!)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Added IE9 support</li>\n<li>Corrected a bunch of HTML validation errors</li>\n<li>Optimized the plugin for better performance (more optimization coming soon)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>New Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>New recurrence rules</li>\n<li>Translated recurrence rules to make it make it human readable and allow for localization</li>\n<li>Globalized the date picker</li>\n<li>Added filter by Categories and Tags to Widget</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"http://theseednetwork.com/blog/2011/11/17/the-all-in-one-event-calendar-1-1/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"125\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"http://theseednetwork.com/blog/2011/11/17/the-all-in-one-event-calendar-1-1/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n	