d allow you to get started developing games on the new social gaming network with the Game Kit Preview.</p><p>iPhone Developer Program members can download iPhone SDK and iPhone OS 4 beta, now available in the <a href=\"http://developer.apple.com/devcenter/ios/\">iOS Dev Center</a>. </p><img style=\"float:right;\" src=\"https://devimages.apple.com.edgekey.net/news/images/feed-images/sdk40.jpg\"/><br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:86;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"\n\n\n\n\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"Keep Your Contact Information Current\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"http://developer.apple.com/news/index.php?id=04062010\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:527:\"As a quick reminder â please make sure you keep your contact information up to date. If we need to reach you by phone or email with questions regarding your app submission, we won\'t be able to do so if the information we have for you isn\'t current. Whenever you need to make changes to your contact information, just log in to the new Member Center, click on the Your Account tab and then select Update Profile. If you need additional assistance regarding updating your contact information, email us at:devprograms@apple.com.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Tue, 06 Apr 2010 15:54:07 PDT\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http: